title: A Holiday Tale of Women's Labor and the Great Resignation
itunes:title: A Holiday Tale of Women's Labor and the Great Resignation
description:
SMNTY takes a look at women's labor, both when it comes to the emotional variety of the holidays and the women making up a majority of the Great Resignation.
